-- NCG Banco to Seek 6 Billion Euros in State Aid, Chairman Says
-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 2012-07-12T16:10:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-12/ncg-banco-to-seek-6-billion-euros-in-state-aid-chairman-says.html
NCG Banco, a Spanish lender, will
seek 6 billion euros ($7.32 billion) in state aid to bolster its
balance sheet.  NCG’s Chairman Jose Maria Castellano gave the amount of the
bank’s request for government support at a news conference in
Santiago de Compostela,  Spain  today. An official for the La
Coruna, Spain-based lender confirmed his remarks in a phone
interview today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Charles Penty in Madrid at 
 cpenty@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at 
 fconnelly@bloomberg.net  